Process called "darwin_x86_64_is_error" takes result as Integer returns Integer:
    Note:
    Check if syscall result indicates error
    BSD syscalls return -1 on error, errno not used directly
    :End Note
    If result is less than 0:
        Return 1  Note: Error
    End If
    Return 0  Note: Success
End Process
